"H-HUEY!?": "Looking for me? ...Of course not. Heh, 'I'm here to kill you' would have been more convincing, don'cha think?"
"I know you saw them. Those... things... that look like me."
"I'm no different. I was just lucky enough to be chosen."
"I get it now... My power is fake, a replica. And there are plenty to replace me."
"Everything was prepared. It was a role that would've been filled with or without me."
"I took a seat on the Council and went around acting like I was one of the three great heroes, never suspecting a thing."
"Clarissa doesn't even speak to me anymore."
"All along, I was manipulated by that person, Luther. They were his words."
"What a fucking joke! It's so funny, I can't even laugh."
"...I don't know how I'm supposed to laugh anymore."
"P-p-peon! You never saw me! Don't you DARE say a word!"
"Wherever crying Photons are near, the great Huey is here!"
"...what th-- gone again!? You there! Claris Claes was standing right here, was she not?"
"2. Just between us, she went that way."
"You have my thanks! Until we meet again!"
